{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Axona, you control a mysterious cube trapped in a strange dimension. Will you be able to find the way out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/Axona_general.gif?t=1738877850\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Roll and Solve</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roll the cube, get the keys and unlock the glyphs to advance to the next level. You will discover new mechanics and solve more complex puzzles as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/Axona_magnetic.gif?t=1738877850\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play at your own pace</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Axona is designed to be a challenging puzzle game but can also be enjoyed in a relaxed manner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/crystal_catch-2.gif?t=1738877850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try to solve each level within a limited number of moves...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/extras/Axona-deploy.gif?t=1738877850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">...Or take as many moves as you need.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738877850","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738877850","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2645950/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738877850","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea